y distances required before Langmuir waves are\nproduced by some electron beams, and the small magnitude of the background\ndensity gradients make closed loops less facilitating for radio emission than\nloops that extend into interplanetary space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 17:31:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Sep 2017 14:19:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-01"}
