ated up only where the magnitudes of the static and\nrotating fields reach the required ratio.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 17:58:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Aug 2017 10:57:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 9 Feb 2018 18:17:50 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 14:36:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-02"}
