t, however. We contextualise our results with those from other\nsemi-analytic models and hydrodynamic simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 18:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2017 06:29:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 16 Aug 2017 04:45:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-17"}
