udget for $H_0$ is dominated by statistical\nerrors due to the small size of the supernova sample, whilst the systematic\ncontribution is dominated by variation in the Cepheid fits, and for the SNe Ia,\nuncertainties in the host galaxy mass dependence and Malmquist bias.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jun 2017 06:23:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-30"}
