 we combine multiple channel\nregimes to classes of channel regimes which share the same fronthaul capacity\nthresholds and as such the same DTB-functional. In total, our analysis\nidentifies four classes; in only three of those edge caching and cloud\nprocessing can provide nontrivial synergestic and non-synergestic performance\ngains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jun 2017 10:11:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-26"}
