ce the new paradigm of angular distortion. Examples will be taken by\nusing some recent publications. The possibilities offers by this approach in\nmechanics and thermodynamics are briefly discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jun 2017 15:38:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Sep 2017 07:07:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-17"}
